description: Le Zheng Yi is an alpha. He has been the highest position of gangster, and his life goal is to become a gangster. Unfortunately, dreams are full and reality is skinny. In the blink of an eye, he became an Omega, and his life goal became not to marry! However, he didn’t know that there was a man beside him who was eyeing up and thinking of marrying him all the time.>
